Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,400)\fad(1000,000)}圣天空战记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是只要坠入爱河每个人都会变得如此孤单?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正拥抱着比黑暗要更深沉的苦楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切必定都是为了让我俩能绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用心凝视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在寒冷的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用泪水来呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你早就给了我 最宝贵的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:12.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 愛したら誰もが こんな孤独になるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:21.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ねえ 暗闇よりも深い苦しみ 抱きしめてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:34.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもが二人 輝くためきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:39.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心で見つめている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:48.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を君を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒い夜も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:15.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙で今呼びかける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:20.03,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束などいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:28.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた大切な強さだから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运的反作用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛,不过就是个小女孩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶莉雅,速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.82,0:02:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放开她!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以过来!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个小鬼真是讲不听
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运增幅器出现异常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶莉雅,把他抓回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这主意不错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚连
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊,我…我好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅,耶莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了,快撒退
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回弗肯大人身边去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟们,手可别停下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也算是种幸运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算遵循占卜的结果,取消了这场婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方依旧会发动攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说我根本就不相信占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德莱甸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我请你做那种事,才会变成这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害你也一起受苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能够原谅我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么下令撒退?弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要违背我的命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容属下斗胆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为再那样下去,那些手下恐怕会有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是难以避免的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是为了我等之理想中的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉,耶莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人,我们不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心娜莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您放心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晓得的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们似乎已经发现小瞳的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定会再次发动攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们现在受到那个叫什么"幸运"的保护着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以连接近他们都办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先解决掉幸运强化兵的幕后黑手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将背叛法尼利亚投靠多伦卡喀的那家伙给…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寨巴哈的军师弗肯·拉克鲁·法尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尼尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我的…王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把碗给摔破了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋带断了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?这是小瞳的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快,他们逃出城了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅露露,你留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要驾驶艾斯嘉科尼去找小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲,请您睁开眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您别留下我一个人,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我重视的人都会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是敢出声我就宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫他们要妨碍我们打猎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说不准我们弄脏这座森林?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是个兽人居然搞不清楚自己的身分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭,贝卢贝卢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会陪着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是金银双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是珍品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以卖到很好的价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要这么做?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了梵的哥哥弗肯吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你想对弗肯报恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.66,0:11:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要将你带回去给弗肯大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你伤成这样,根本没办法再行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会跟亚连他们商量的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一定能够体谅的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你并不是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是要我投降吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我相信你的话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.23,0:12:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有弗肯大人能让我信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人喜欢弗肯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,港□?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女的身影正逐渐浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你立刻派幸运强化兵过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她尚未恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装置运作得相当顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别为我操心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您,让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运强化兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想说如果要逃走,就一定得经由港□
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦迪斯,将库鲁杰特准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:13:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:13:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在没空应付你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是因为"幸运"吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就无法靠近现在的她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里?弗肯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能再回去弗肯那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你就搭这艘船,逃到远方去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体被奇怪的机械改造
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此变得这样虚弱残破
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是为了自己喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样还是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住□
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…这样绝对很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你就是不懂?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心中潜藏的不安心情,将招来令人难过的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己的意念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的意念必有实现的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要相信…自己的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不害怕吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接下来会受到什么样的凌迟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然害怕,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不逃?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你想逃,明明就逃得掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信自己的意念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你并不是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能为弗肯大人奉献一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得心满意足了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么会晓得我们所在?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯,你在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊,快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你能了解的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.85,0:17:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念起来真好听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅\N什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是弗肯大人帮我取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在会碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走,耶莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到弗肯大人的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瞳,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯,你给我出来!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你就是不懂呢?梵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们创造新世界之日就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后的战役
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你就是不懂呢?梵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人,这里由我们来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运强化兵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太不知好歹了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人如此为你着想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是那么的为你着想,为何你就是不明白?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不原谅让弗肯大人伤心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不原谅!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮游要塞爆炸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵,娜莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人,请您快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别在意我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能遇见您已是万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能够在您的目送下死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗肯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是反作用吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经由人工强化的幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了名为不幸的反作用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次的实验已经带来丰硕的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是"解答"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我得到了未知的解答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我等的命运方程式…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你错了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.03,0:21:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王兄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.13,0:22:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把剑放下,梵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:22:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才不是我的兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.78,0:23:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑翼的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:57.09,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月儿彼方蓝色探照灯照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:05.54,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然降临的天使 你究竟是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:13.17,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的门扉即将开启　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.48,0:22:19.32,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放过这令人兴奋的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:21.68,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:26.69,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那燃烧般的神秘双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:30.53,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真无邪的笑容让我倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:34.33,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞳眸深处的暗示只传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:38.34,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了无止尽的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:41.84,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内心的鼓动无法抑制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:49.31,ED_CHINESE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想带着你一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:57.08,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月の向こう　蒼い Search light　重なる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:05.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然舞い降りたAngel　そう　君は誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:13.17,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　運命の　扉が開く　So just fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.48,0:22:19.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸騒ぎするこの瞬間を逃がさない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:21.68,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop,baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:26.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焼けそうな　君の Mystic eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:30.52,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邪気な笑顔で　Breaking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:34.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君だけに　瞳の奥の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.40,0:22:38.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てない　旅は始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:41.84,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止まらない　胸の鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:49.31,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を　さらっていきたい


